bruce, for the HB you need to write data to $7000 to control the
motors.  see appendix B of the 6.270 manual at

  http://el.www.media.mit.edu/projects/handy-board/techdocs/

and also the HB FAQ

  http://el.www.media.mit.edu/projects/handy-board/faq/

fred

